premise_source_doc_sentence: The Scream series has received several awards , including a Saturn Award for Best Actress and an MTV Movie Award for Best Performance for Neve Campbell and a Saturn Award for Best Horror Film for Scream .
The film series has been the recipient of several awards including a Saturn Award for Best Actress and MTV Movie Award for Best Female Performance for Campbell and Best Horror Film for Scream .
Kevin Williamson wrote Scream , Scream 2 and Scream 4 but scheduling commitments meant he could provide only notes for Scream 3 , with writing duties instead helmed by Ehren Kruger .

The series consists of four films , Scream  (  1996  )  , Scream 2  (  1997  )  , Scream 3  (  2000  )  and most recently Scream 4  (  2011  )  , with all of the films being directed by Wes Craven and scored by Marco Beltrami .
